#: src/Dialogs/dlgGestureHelp.cpp:16
msgid ""
"# Gesture Navigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen "
"mode\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan "
"mode\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby "
"waypoints."
msgstr ""
"# Navigacija gestais\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar palaiko lietimo gestus žemėlapyje:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Perbraukti aukštyn** (U): priartinti\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Perbraukti žemyn** (D): tolinti\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Perbraukite dešinėn** (R): ankstesnis "
"ekrano režimas\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Perbraukti kairėn** (L): kito ekrano "
"režimas\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Aukštyn-žemyn** (UD): automatinis "
"mastelio keitimas\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Žemyn aukštyn** (DU): meniu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Žemyn-dešinėn** (DR): išsami informacija "
"apie kelio tašką\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Iš apačios į kairę** (DL): alternatyvos\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Dešinėn žemyn** (RD): užduočių tvarkyklė\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Aukštyn-dešinėn-žemyn** (URD): analizė\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Kairė-žemyn-dešinėn** (LDR): "
"kontrolinis sąrašas\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Aukštyn-dešinėn-žemyn-kairėn** "
"(URDL): panoraminis režimas\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Kairė-žemyn-dešinėn-žemyn-kairė** "
"(LDRDL): būsena\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Aukštyn-kairėn-žemyn-dešinėn** "
"(ULDR): spartusis meniu\n"
"\n"
"Ilgai paspauskite žemėlapį, kad įjungtumėte panoraminį režimą. Norėdami "
"pamatyti netoliese esančius kelio taškus, palieskite, kol veikia panoraminis "
"režimas."

